HEADWORD: Campanulales
<hw>Campanulales</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an order of plants which
includes the <fam>Campanulaceae</fam>; <fam>Lobeliaceae</fam>;
<fam>Cucurbitaceae</fam>; <fam>Goodeniaceae</fam>;
<fam>Stylidiaceae</fam>; <fam>Calyceraceae</fam>; and
<fam>Compositae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> order <ord>Campanulales</ord>.</syn>⟦br⟧
